Stunty's Lair~
You find yourself in an open crypt which seems out of place compared
to the other rooms in the tower.  In the faint light which seeps under
the door, you can see several empty coffins, their lids cast aside.  With
a fleeting moment of fear, you wonder what happened to their previous
occupants.  At the far wall, you see one coffin that seems to stand out
from the rest.  Rich, polished mahogany with tarnished silver fittings.  It
is most luxurious, for a corpse.  A wooden door to the north allows you to
flee this place of dread.
~
